Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.82,difLang,,0000,0000,0000,,{F}Da nisu na medenom mesecu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:16.78,nodame,,0000,0000,0000,,Idemo, Nodame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.28,nodame,,0000,0000,0000,,U redu, Čiaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:32.46,nodame,,0000,0000,0000,,To je bazilika Sakre ker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:34.88,nodame,,0000,0000,0000,,Podseća me na prošlost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:47.98,nodame,,0000,0000,0000,,Konačno sam se vratio u Pariz.
