Comment: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:11.95,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,From Tokyo to Paris,
Comment: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.89,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,and from Paris to Tokyo,
Comment: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:17.85,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,there would always be music.
Comment: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:25.89,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,And in Paris, we'll study together.
Comment: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:28.58,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other since childhood.
Comment: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:32.65,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,We would go to the piano classes next door
Comment: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:36.38,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of the marketplace,
Comment: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:39.02,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,and we would play hopscotch and dodgeball
Comment: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:43.22,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,in the neighborhood park.
Comment: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.40,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it was over.
Comment: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:51.75,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,They were the best years of our lives,
Comment: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:56.27,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,unaffected by worries.
Comment: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.47,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,From Tokyo to Paris,
Comment: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.48,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,and from Paris to Tokyo,
Comment: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:06.92,NodameED,,0000,0000,0000,,there would always be music.
